<SLUG> BC-Australia-Gas Shortage, 3rd Ld-Writethru </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Victoria state faces up to two weeks without gas as industry shuts
</HEADLINE>
down
 &UR; Eds: UPDATES in 2nd graf with gas shortage possibly lasting two
weeks &QL; 

