<HEADLINE>
Gold in Hong Kong closes higher
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   HONG KONG (AP) _ Gold in Hong Kong closed at U.S. dlrs 293.95 an
ounce on Monday, up 20 U.S. cents from Saturday's close of U.S.
dlrs 293.75 an ounce.
 &UR; _0_ 	   
</TEXT>
