are expelled aid workers. AP Photo ISL201.
	   _FEA-RUSSIA-FOSTERING CHILDREN. Moscow couple tries to break
cycle of abandonment. AP Photos NY308-312.
	   _FEA-AFGHANISTAN-AILING HEALTH. Afghanistan's health care in
critical condition. AP Photo NY307.
