Ian Wright scores as West Ham wins 1-0
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   LONDON (AP) _ Ian Wright's goal in the 61st minute Monday lifted
West Ham over struggling Southampton 1-0, moving the Hammers into
fourth place with 12 points.
	   West Ham now has the same point total as Derby and Wimbledon but
trails both on goal-difference. Aston Villa leads the Premier
League with 17 points.
