 &UR; FEATURES: Business and Finance
	   SANTIAGO, Chile _ Seventeen years after privatizing its pension
funds system, Chile may have some advise for other nations adopting
or planning a similar change. But the Chilean experience, while
generally considered successful, also needs corrections, including
cutting management costs, experts say. FEA-CHILE-PENSION FUNDS. By
Eduardo Gallardo. To move as wire time permits.
