<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Yen-Dollar </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Dollar higher against yen in Tokyo
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   TOKYO (AP) _ The U.S. dollar was trading at 136.35 yen on the
Tokyo foreign exchange market at 9 a.m. (0000 GMT) Tuesday, up 0.63
yen from its level of 135.72 yen as of 5 p.m. (0800 GMT) Monday.
</TEXT>
(PROFILE
(WS SL:BC-Yen-Dollar; CT:f; 
(REG:ASIA;)
