<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 09/28/1998 20:15:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
w1705 &Cx1f; wstm-
r i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-Japan-Recession'sCasu     09-28 0754
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Japan-Recession's Casualties,0753 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Island's economic woes demonstrate fallout from Japan's bank
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; RETRANSMITTING to delete sidebar Economy &QL; 
crisis &QL; 
 &UR; With Japan-Recession Facts &QL; 
 &UR; AP Photo TOK105 &QL; 
 &UR; By TODD ZAUN &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

<TEXT>
	   SAPPORO, Japan (AP) _ Torao Kano thought he had enough money put
aside for a comfortable retirement, without having to depend on his
